OL,3,C'A hole in my heart': Mum's plea after
OL,4,Cson, 26, dies as ketamine deaths soar
OL,6,FDeaths due to illicit ketamine use
OL,7,Fhave increased twenty-fold since 2014,
OL,8,Faccording to a new analysis of
OL,9,Fcoroners' reports, as Sejal Karia
OL,10,Freports for ITV News.
OL,12,FA mother whose son died in the shower
OL,13,Fafter taking ketamine is calling for
OL,14,Fthe drug to be reclassified, as new
OL,15,Ffigures show a surge in related deaths.
OL,17,FClare Rogers, who's from Atherstone in
OL,18,FWarwickshire, lost her son Rian in
OL,19,F2023. He was just 26 when he was found
OL,20,Fdead in his shower, killed by a dose
OL,21,F30 times stronger than he realised.
