OL,3,C'A hole in my heart': Mum's plea after
OL,4,Cson, 26, dies as ketamine deaths soar
OL,6,FNew research shows deaths linked to
OL,7,Fketamine have risen sharply - from
OL,8,Fjust six in 2014 to more than 120 in
OL,9,F2023. Since the late 1990s, nearly 700
OL,10,Fdeaths have been recorded.
OL,12,FKetamine is a licensed anaesthetic,
OL,13,Fbut its illegal use is increasing
OL,14,Famong young people.
OL,16,FIt has also been linked to the deaths
OL,17,Fof celebrities including Friends star
OL,18,FMatthew Perry and RuPaul's Drag Race
OL,19,Fwinner, The Vivienne.
