OL,3,C'A hole in my heart': Mum's plea after
OL,4,Cson, 26, dies as ketamine deaths soar
OL,6,FMs Rogers is urging the government to
OL,7,Freclassify ketamine as a Class A drug,
OL,8,Fmaking possession and supply subject
OL,9,Fto tougher penalties.
OL,11,FBut experts say that move alone won't
OL,12,Fsave lives.
OL,14,F"We need to reduce the demand, and
OL,15,Fthat's not by criminalising them.
OL,16,FThat's by getting (users) the help and
OL,17,Fthe treatment they need," said Dr
OL,18,FCaroline Copeland, a pharmacology and
OL,19,Ftoxicology lecturer at King's College
OL,20,FLondon.
