OL,3,C'A hole in my heart': Mum's plea after
OL,4,Cson, 26, dies as ketamine deaths soar
OL,6,FMeanwhile, the government has said it
OL,7,Fis asking for new advice from the
OL,8,FExpert Committee on Drug Dependence
OL,9,Faround the classification of drugs.
OL,11,FSpeaking in July, the then-Home
OL,12,FSecretary Yvette Cooper MP said she
OL,13,Fwas well aware of growing problems
OL,14,Frelated to ketamine use.
OL,16,F"I am really worried about the things
OL,17,Fwe've seen with ketamine, and some of
OL,18,Fthe serious and escalating
OL,19,Fconsequences (of using it)," she said.
